@node leaderbydefault "What's this leader-by-default nonsense?"
  
  As I have mentioned several time already (and you have read several times
if you read this more or less in the order  I write it), Bård "Scarycat" is
our leader-by-default. The reason I call  him that is simply that he became
the leader because he started  the  whole  thing  (see "@{"How did it start?" link history}")
and, presumably, because noone else wanted the job!
  [Actually, of late (summer 95) I've been so active with shaking the other
members out of their sleep,  some of them have suggested that *I* should be
the leader... Don't know, there may be some changes next time we meet...]

@endnode

