@node warlockname "What does that stupid name stand for?"

  To paraphrase the warlock for a change (the other nodes quote him more or
less directly), he picked the main part  of his name because he has "always
loved magical dudes", and because  there  have been so many warlocks before
he decided to number himself¹, and  seven  is supposed to be a magical num-
ber. "So there, that's all there is to it!"

¹Of course it has nothing to do with the  fact that picking a name that be-
gins with a number would have  put  him  first  in  a machine-sorted member
list, but I tricked him - the  list  at  the  start  of this file is sorted
manually, and in my book 7 begins with "Se". Ha! ;-)

@endnode

