@node wontolla "Who is Won-Tolla?"

  Ragnar "Won-Tolla" Fyri (12.01.@{"57" link 57}) is the group's first active programmer
(Okay, so it's just Amos, but at  least  that's a beginning...). He did all
the programming for the intro  and  the  slide  show, and is also the third
"artist" represented in this slide show. He drew his own logo and persuaded
Imagine to come up with the  two  following  pictures  (Eye  and CreAm With
Coffee... or something like that). [Actually  they are both test renderings
of unfinished projects, but Scarycat  wanted  to  include them anyway! Look
for finished (?) versions in later publications...]
  When it was  found that we  could use  some more pictures,  he heroically
descended into  his old  disk pile and came  up with a two more pictures, a
variant of what later became his logo (and an exercise in gradients)  and a
kind of satellite picture that started as an experiment with brush effects!
  
                            @{"Where does he live?" link wontollahome}
                 @{"What does that stupid name stand for?" link wontollaname} ;-)
